subject: Baseball
lead_paragraph: Derek Jeter became the eighth Yankee to reach his 2,000th career hit, joining Lou Gehrig, Babe Ruth, Mickey Mantle, Bernie Williams, Joe DiMaggio, Don Mattingly and Yogi Berra.
